{"tid":900324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"只鬆開手3秒 深圳兩歲幼童衝出馬路遭貨車輾斃","createTime":"2018-11-13T06:54:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-13T14:44:04.000Z","uid":75969,"like":394,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":124,"replies":[{"pid":"0f4bda41af4b7cd1608ea0a8680c299ece67bc90","tid":900324,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T06:54:23.000Z","msg":"片<br />\n<a href=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181113/__2018111313004260868.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181113%2F__2018111313004260868.mp4&d=LW9BPaYju2cXFN7lLAFZbpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=e9502538\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181113%2F__2018111313004260868.mp4&h=1c4082cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181113/__2018111313004260868.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181113/_2018111313004236488.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181113%2F_2018111313004236488.jpg&h=1c4cbd0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n只是疏忽了3秒，換來沉重的代價！11月9日上午11點07分左右，一輛貨車在寶安區福海街道塘尾社區行駛時，路旁突然跑出一名兩歲男童，該車右側車輪輾過摔倒在地的幼童身上，男童送院經搶救後不幸身亡。深圳交警表示，經調取閉路電視片段，發現男童練某屬於學齡前兒童，其母親在看護時沒有盡到看護的義務，導致練某從路旁跑到馬路上。<br />\n<br />\n當地警方指，張姓男子上周五（9日）上午11點07分開着輕型貨車，在寶安區福海接福路由西向東行駛，沒想到一名練姓男童突然從右側衝出，當場遭貨車右前輪、右後輪接連輾過。<br />\n<br />\n事發後，深圳交警將影片分享到微博，從影片可見，該名母親帶着兩歲兒子在玩耍，不料才鬆手短短3秒，男童就衝出馬路遭貨車輾過，母親立即追上去，可惜已經太遲了，目睹這一幕當場嚇傻，孩子送院經急救回天乏術。目前相關單位還在進一步劃分釐清責任。<br />\n<br />\n當地警方表示這是一場「鬼探頭」（視線死角）引起的悲劇，當時母親沒有盡到看護義務，導致男童衝到馬路身亡，希望家長「一定要看好孩子」。<br />\n<br />\n許多微博網友看完後，紛紛留言表示：「小孩不幸，司機可憐，這媽是怎麼當的」、「這個位置真的看不到，開過車都知道」、「司機有點冤啊」、「心疼司機，真正的受害者」、「自己都不在乎，誰還在乎，司機真是時運不濟」掀起熱議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/863260\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F863260&d=LW9BPaYju2cXFN7lLAFZbpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=b1167941\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F863260&h=fe680918\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/863260</a>"},{"pid":"bda6947ecdac57d3e723ff4f75c7053b87386a74","tid":900324,"uid":29702,"like":33,"dislike":4,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T06:55:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1287fcf3f24a35aa4a7428608374036032f63d5f","tid":900324,"uid":143499,"like":145,"dislike":8,"score":137,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T06:55:34.000Z","msg":"Chi-Na ese -1<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a8edd7be0ecfdd7321e7b4790fa6dc5c02b6d52","tid":900324,"uid":185184,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T06:56:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0efce3cb9b011d7865ad717108ea2d728c79b384","tid":900324,"uid":60287,"like":252,"dislike":4,"score":248,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T06:57:29.000Z","msg":"刷仆住去刷首抽"},{"pid":"4f4c644ff1ead169065f2e2196cb8a9e0decd4f7","tid":900324,"uid":60287,"like":30,"dislike":3,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T06:57:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><del>刷</del>仆住去刷首抽</blockquote>"},{"pid":"1c8d7c7a7ce5bf62cf98d028fe53a2ed8abc7daf","tid":900324,"uid":177047,"like":339,"dislike":5,"score":334,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T06:58:00.000Z","msg":"個幼蝗知自己咩料，可能有前世記憶，知自己做左蝗就重刷首抽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a0c39dd27bd3142bc40c5519ce501df8bb9d01","tid":900324,"uid":89514,"like":102,"dislike":2,"score